{
  "stem": "8786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Instead of sending us-- he knew that everybody from the ghetto will be sent to Auschwitz, so he was-- he was smart enough or good enough to take out all the manpower was from 14 to 60, young boys from 14 up to 60.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That means most of them were 14 to 19 and 55 to 60, something like that, both extreme groups.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were called the ghetto battalions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were taken in by-- we had to walk in from our town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the last time I saw my-- the rest of my family, my mother and my younger brother, who was a little bit shorter, because this-- this army officer, he just took and-- come on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You go this way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You go this way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not like Mengele, but just judged it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My brother was a little bit shorter than I am, about a year younger than me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was 16 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was 15 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was the last time I saw them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were marching in that same day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was late afternoon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- started to march to a town, which is called Jelsava.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's in Slovaki, in Slovenska today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's spelled Y-O-L-S-V-A.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was like many, many-- from many, many ghettos, the-- these forced laborers were collected over there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is like a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] point where many, many hundreds of people got together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had over there a large barracks, army barracks, and it was full of these forced laborers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from there, they organized 300, 300, 300, which was called a battalion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were sent out right away, even though we were not what you call the normal age group for the labor going out to the-- to the battlefield.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
